1
00:12:00,887 --> 00:12:02,055
Greetings

2
00:12:03,682 --> 00:12:05,142
May I have...

3
00:12:06,935 --> 00:12:08,311
espresso.

4
00:12:09,104 --> 00:12:10,188
and...

5
00:12:11,731 --> 00:12:13,150
and...

6
00:12:14,276 --> 00:12:15,444
croissant

7
00:12:17,821 --> 00:12:18,905
espresso.

8
00:12:31,751 --> 00:12:32,252
Yes.

9
00:12:48,685 --> 00:12:50,812
You have to be careful.

10
00:12:51,021 --> 00:12:52,772
Keep your eyes open in Rome.

11
00:12:58,528 --> 00:12:59,613
Sugar.

12
00:13:15,795 --> 00:13:18,048
We'll take care of you. Ok?
Don't worry.

13
00:13:59,339 --> 00:14:00,799
Is everything ok?

14
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,142
Do you have your wallet?

15
00:24:42,773 --> 00:24:44,358
Thank you.

16
00:24:45,818 --> 00:24:47,528
He's amazing.

17
00:24:47,737 --> 00:24:48,863
He's alright.

18
00:24:49,405 --> 00:24:50,448
Alright?

19
00:24:50,656 --> 00:24:51,574
What're you talking about?

20
00:24:51,782 --> 00:24:53,117
I can sing better.

21
00:24:53,284 --> 00:24:54,744
Are you crazy? He's incredible!

22
00:24:54,952 --> 00:24:56,329
I'm telling you...

23
00:24:56,495 --> 00:24:56,954
Show me!

24
00:24:57,163 --> 00:24:57,997
Go!

25
00:24:58,206 --> 00:24:59,874
Go up there?

26
00:25:00,291 --> 00:25:01,250
Yes!

27
00:25:01,876 --> 00:25:03,127
No, no.

28
00:33:45,149 --> 00:33:46,024
What?

29
00:33:49,403 --> 00:33:50,571
Impossible.

30
00:33:53,532 --> 00:33:55,367
Go away. Bye.

31
00:34:02,958 --> 00:34:04,251
Make me a coffee, please.

32
00:34:04,585 --> 00:34:05,419
And find me Gia.

33
00:34:17,514 --> 00:34:19,099
If you answered my calls,
I wouldn't have to come here.

34
00:34:19,308 --> 00:34:20,893
I know, but today
is not a day to talk.

35
00:34:21,101 --> 00:34:22,186
We need to talk.

36
00:34:22,770 --> 00:34:24,688
Very, very busy. Excuse me.

37
00:36:00,659 --> 00:36:01,493
Here's a flower!

38
00:36:12,337 --> 00:36:14,798
Who is he? Does he speak Italian?

39
00:36:14,965 --> 00:36:17,384
No, he's American.
He doesn't understand Italian.

40
00:36:26,101 --> 00:36:27,561
But we're just friends.

41
00:36:28,437 --> 00:36:29,646
No, I swear. Really!

42
00:40:16,581 --> 00:40:18,250
Can you paint a portrait
of both of us?

43
00:40:19,251 --> 00:40:21,503
We came here on a tandem bike.

44
01:04:48,802 --> 01:04:51,096
Good luck at the Palio, Andrea!

45
01:04:51,305 --> 01:04:52,097
Thank you, Giglio!

46
01:04:52,306 --> 01:04:53,432
We will win!

47
01:05:33,388 --> 01:05:34,806
Gia, how are you?

48
01:05:34,973 --> 01:05:36,350
Good, good. Thank you.

49
01:05:36,516 --> 01:05:38,560
I wanted to talk to you the other day.

50
01:05:38,769 --> 01:05:40,187
I had things to do.

51
01:06:53,552 --> 01:06:56,847
Andrea, can we say grace, please?

52
01:06:57,264 --> 01:06:59,391
Sure, it's a good thing.

53
01:07:04,312 --> 01:07:06,690
Lord, we thank you for this food.

54
01:07:07,399 --> 01:07:09,568
Bless this wonderful family...

55
01:07:10,026 --> 01:07:12,112
And all our new friends.

56
01:07:14,781 --> 01:07:18,034
We also add a little prayer
for our horse, Mistico.

57
01:07:18,368 --> 01:07:21,997
Tomorrow, may he conclude
the Palio as a victor!

58
01:08:05,582 --> 01:08:08,084
You always did have a hard
time seeing anything through.

59
01:08:08,293 --> 01:08:10,003
What did you just say?

60
01:08:10,295 --> 01:08:11,630
I guess that makes two of us!

61
01:08:11,838 --> 01:08:13,715
Are you really giving up the cafe?

62
01:08:13,924 --> 01:08:17,219
Yes, because now you'll have
no reason to see me anymore.

63
01:08:55,340 --> 01:08:56,716
May the best horse win!

64
01:20:19,315 --> 01:20:20,233
Good Luck.

65
01:26:01,907 --> 01:26:03,659
Vincenzo, I already signed the lease.

66
01:26:03,868 --> 01:26:05,953
You didn't have to come here.

67
01:26:07,705 --> 01:26:09,164
I came to say hello...

68
01:26:09,415 --> 01:26:10,833
And to make you an offer.

69
01:26:11,333 --> 01:26:13,961
But why, Vincenzo? I lost the bet.

70
01:26:14,169 --> 01:26:14,920
I know.

71
01:26:15,546 --> 01:26:17,798
But I can't keep the cafe forever.

72
01:26:21,135 --> 01:26:21,802
Thank you.

73
01:26:22,052 --> 01:26:23,053
Thank you, Vincenzo.

74
01:26:23,512 --> 01:26:24,805
You better go get him.

75
01:26:25,556 --> 01:26:28,142
No, it's too late. He's already gone.

76
01:26:29,184 --> 01:26:30,227
He's out there waiting

77
01:26:30,436 --> 01:26:31,812
for you on a motorcycle.

78
01:26:33,397 --> 01:26:34,148
Go!

79
01:27:29,745 --> 01:27:30,913
This is beautiful.

80
01:28:16,250 --> 01:28:17,292
Miss...

81
01:28:17,793 --> 01:28:19,503
No smoking here.
